    procedureSteps: '1. Schedule meeting minimum 3 days before bulk cut date.\n2. Invite Merchandiser, Cutting Head, Sewing Chief, QA Head, and IE.\n3. Review buyer comments on the approved sample.\n4. Discuss critical operations, fabric behavior (shrinkage/skewing), and special machinery needs.\n5. Sign off on PP Meeting minute document.',
