    responsibility: 'Section Supervisor',
    procedureSteps: '1. Use standard template to mark button/hole positions with vanishing chalk.\n2. Operator matches mark to machine guide.\n3. Make buttonhole, check knife sharpness (must cut cleanly without fraying).\n4. Attach button using cross or parallel stitch as per spec.\n5. Check stitch locking (knotting) on the back to prevent unraveling.',
